timeline.bodyText:
I'd prefer to write these boolean expressions in a more boolean way, i.e.:
granted = granted || actionCheck;
bwcGrantMappingUpdate = bwcGrantMappingUpdate || bwcMappingActionCheck;
A minor benefit is that they short-circuit.
Also might wanna consider pulling it up into the above if check since the values do not change unless actionCheck or bwcMappingActionCheck is true.

